{"tid":1456613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤好唔撤好任務完成就得 唔好自亂陣腳 下一步係組織連續性罷工","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:43:59.000Z","uid":49774,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8086d9f18a6593ba604bc03d377adbc5b8d67b25","tid":1456613,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"罷工唔可以好似上次咁鳩做<br />\n機場既外國關注已經做得<br />\n我覺得係時候要貼地返 將比tvb洗腦既人救出黎<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動都要做得有意義<br />\n有巴打講過可以合作地入車廂做811精華廣播<br />\n只要罷工人數足夠<br />\n每一班列車每一個車廂都要嘗試廣播還原真相<br />\n我就預左有人挑機 有辯論 事實會更愈辯愈明<br />\n但起碼我地係合情合理合法先<br />\n我覺得呢種形式引黎既點響同效果比起佔路機場集會更大<br />\n希望冇巴絲可以組織下"},{"pid":"4a1b57d08e040b4ffe7914ab6396df2d066e63d9","tid":1456613,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3ba96fd162542371d6d0b3b793dee585c368ba","tid":1456613,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d12cdbbca47911991299247ab3f70fe39c9ead","tid":1456613,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"罷工香港唔work"},{"pid":"caddd6f05cd00b1c0036bf8e97547ebb46e02444","tid":1456613,"uid":293308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"借個靓位<br />\n<br />\n【大 反 擊 !】全 港 大 罷 課 ! ! !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1453518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1453518</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b9d472260405aa9490d2a4bd01608fa1adbc94b","tid":1456613,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d12cdbbca47911991299247ab3f70fe39c9ead","tid":1456613,"uid"